# ngx_http_waf_module - social / monitor / feed / HTTP-library User-Agent sigs
#
# $waf_type = bot. Flag-only: surfaced for the operator, never blocked by
# waf_bot_block. Covers link-preview unfurlers, SEO/monitoring bots, feed
# readers and generic HTTP client libraries. One case-insensitive PCRE2
# fragment per line; regex metacharacters ('/', '^', '.') are significant.
#
# NEVER add a bare 'bot'/'spider'/'crawl'/'Mozilla' token: massive false
# positives. Keep tokens to distinctive product / library names.

# -- social / link-preview unfurlers ----------------------------------------
facebookexternalhit
Twitterbot
LinkedInBot
Slackbot
Discordbot
TelegramBot
redditbot

# -- SEO / monitoring -------------------------------------------------------
AhrefsBot
SemrushBot
MJ12bot
dotbot
UptimeRobot
Pingdom
Feedly

# -- generic HTTP client libraries ------------------------------------------
python-requests
Go-http-client
curl/
^Java/
okhttp
axios
Scrapy
libwww-perl
Wget
Apache-HttpClient
